title: Beverly.Hills.Pawn.S02E09.McQueen.and.Masquerades.(Jan.26.2014).
description:
Beverly Hills Pawn, Season 2, Episode 9.

First aired on January 26, 2014.

Title: McQueen & Masquerades

Description: A client wants to sell a piece of Michael Jackson's wardrobe; Patrick Muldoon brings in a truck once owned by Steve McQueen; a piece that belonged to Elizabeth Taylor; a jacket worn by Barbra Streisand in 'Yentl'; Jamie Walters' guitar.

Note: The episode number (#9) is not from TVRage as there is no description of this particular episode on TVRage; so I just took the next number after the last aired episode.  This looks to me as a lost episode from season one; so don't be surprised if the next aired episode also have the same number 9.


Format: x264, MP4.
